Revision history for Perl extension HTML::FormatData

0.10  Mon May 16 2005 
	- cleaned up docs for CPAN release

0.09  Wed Apr 20 2005 
	- fixed bug in format_text() that would run jobs out of proper order

0.08  Tue Mar 29 2005 
	- broke out MasonX::App::Format into seperate package, HTML::FormatData
	- implemented OO interface
	- added reformat_date() from MasonX/App.pm

0.07  Mon Feb 7 2005  
	- shortcut for RFC-822 date format added

0.06  Thu Nov 4 2004
	- added new text cleaning routines; fixed a bug in clean_whitespace

0.05  Mon Aug 23 2004
	- renamed FormatText.pm to Format.pmin preparation of adding new functions
	- changed args passed to format_text from hashref to hash
	- added parse_date and format_date functions

0.04  Wed Apr 21 2004
	-added clean_high_ascii() to convert problem characters in Word docs

0.03  Mon Apr 12 2004
	- removed dependence on XML::Comma for XML encode and decode

0.02 Fri Apr 9 2004
	- added truncate_no_ellipses job

0.01  Wed Feb 25 2004
	- first packaged release. O-O rewrite of old WebApp package.
